  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Plastic Tooling Designer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>MEIBAN MOLD MANUFACTURE PTE LTD</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Analyze product designs to optimize for manufacturability and cost efficiency through Design for Manufacturing (DFM) principles</li><li>Develop detailed 3D and 2D tool designs using AutoCAD and Unigraphics to meet precise plastic injection molding requirements</li><li>Construct comprehensive mold design layouts and lead mold design review meetings to ensure design accuracy and feasibility</li><li>Design precision plastic injection molds aligned with product specifications and production standards</li><li>Manage mold projects by coordinating closely with internal teams and external customers to address mold design-related issues</li><li>Prepare detailed bills of materials and maintain thorough documentation in both hardcopy and digital formats for traceability</li><li>Participate in First-Off Tool reviews to evaluate tool readiness and suitability for production launch</li><li>Evaluate and analyze tooling issues to identify root causes and implement effective solutions</li><li>Develop complex mold designs through to manufacturing release, ensuring readiness for production</li><li>Apply knowledge of plastics and elastomers to inform mold design decisions and material selection</li><li>Utilize expertise in 3D modeling and Geometric Dimensioning and Tolerancing (GD&T) to ensure design precision and compliance</li><li>Communicate effectively with stakeholders at all levels through clear verbal and written communication</li><li>Collaborate as a proactive team member, demonstrating willingness to take on additional responsibilities as needed</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned to support operational and project goals</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in designing Liquid Silicone Rubber (LSR) molds and packaging molds</li></ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 3,
